      "type": "string",
      "content": "<div style='color: var(--explainColor); background: var(--explainBg); padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid var(--strongColor);'>\n  <h4 style='color: var(--strongColor); margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 15px;'>Complex Conjugate Product</h4>\n  \n  <div style='margin-bottom: 12px;'>\n    <strong style='color: var(--strongColor);'>Step 1: Identify the Conjugate</strong><br>\n    For z = 7 - 4i, the conjugate is z̄ = 7 + 4i\n  </div>\n\n  <div style='margin-bottom: 12px;'>\n    <strong style='color: var(--strongColor);'>Step 2: Multiply Complex Numbers</strong><br>\n    (7 - 4i)(7 + 4i) = 7(7) + 7(4i) - 4i(7) - 4i(4i)<br>\n    = 49 + 28i - 28i - 16i²\n  </div>\n\n  <div style='margin-bottom: 12px;'>\n    <strong style='color: var(--strongColor);'>Step 3: Simplify</strong><br>\n    <div style='background: rgba(0,0,0,0.05); padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 8px 0; text-align: center;'>\n      49 + 28i - 28i - 16(-1)<br>\n      = 49 + 16<br>\n      = 65\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div style='background: var(--cAnsBg); color: var(--cAns); padding: 12px; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid var(--cAns); margin-top: 15px;'>\n    <strong>✓ Final Answer:</strong> The product is 65\n  </div>\n</div>"
